com.basho.riak.client.api.cap

Enum ConflictResolverFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ConflictResolverFactory>
      • com.basho.riak.client.api.cap.ConflictResolverFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ConflictResolverFactory>

    public enum ConflictResolverFactory
extends Enum<ConflictResolverFactory>
    Simple factory for ConflictResolver objects.

    When you have multiple writers there may be multiple versions of the same object stored in Riak. When fetching all of these will be returned and you will need to resolve the conflict.

    To facilitate this, you can store an instance of the ConflictResolver in this factory for a class. It will then be used by the FetchValue.Response to resolve a set a of siblings to a single object.

    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Brian Roach
